## ⚛️ Reactive Storage Guidelines
- Use React context for global state, wrapped with custom hooks.
- Avoid prop drilling by providing `useX` hooks.
- Keep state serializable to support time-travel debugging.
- Reference existing patterns before introducing new ones.
